{"article_id":"7NIa14RDcapmUEOh","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"US Attorney General Jeff Sessions has responded to Donald Trump 's latest attack on him","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"by insisting","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"that the justice department","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"he heads","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"will not bend to political pressure .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"The apparent rebuke of Mr Trump came","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"after the president said","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"Mr Sessions was not in control of his department .","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"Mr Trump has been vociferous in his criticism of the Department of Justice .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"He has been particularly riled by its handling of the inquiry into Russian interference in the 2016 election .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"Mr Sessions , an early supporter of Mr Trump 's campaign , has stepped aside from that inquiry","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"to avoid a potential conflict of interest","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"and handed control to his deputy , Rod Rosenstein .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"That decision by Mr Sessions , and the ongoing progress of the inquiry under special counsel Robert Mueller","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"- which is also reportedly now looking into","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"whether Mr Trump has attempted to obstruct justice -","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"have provoked frequent outbursts from the president , both in person and on his Twitter feed .","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"The president remains insistent","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"that there was no collusion between his campaign and the Russian government ,","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"and denies","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"he has attempted to obstruct justice .","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"After the latest exchanges , two key Republican senators signalled","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"that they would support Mr Trump","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"if he were to fire Mr Sessions after the November mid-term elections .","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"However , other Republicans told Politico","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"they thought","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"this would be a bad move","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"and said","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"they were standing by the attorney general .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"`` I took control of the Department of Justice the day","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"I was sworn in , ''","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"the attorney general said in a statement .","depth":5},{"id":32,"text":"`` While I am attorney general ,","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"the actions of the Department of Justice will not be improperly influenced by political considerations .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"`` I demand the highest standards ,","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"and","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"where they are not met ,","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"I take action . ''","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"He added :","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"`` No nation has a more talented , more dedicated group of law enforcement investigators and prosecutors than the United States .","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"`` I am proud to serve with them","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"and proud of the work","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"we have done","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"in successfully advancing the rule of law . ''","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"Previously , Mr Sessions had been largely non-committal","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"following criticism of him by the president ,","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"who appears to believe","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"that Mr Sessions should have shown him greater loyalty","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"instead of recusing himself from the Russia inquiry .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"In an earlier interview with the Fox and Friends programme , Mr Trump said :","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"`` I put in an attorney general","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"that never took control of the justice department .","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"Jeff Sessions never took control of the justice department","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"and it 's a sort of an incredible thing . ''","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"Turning to the Russia inquiry ,","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"the president said :","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"`` Jeff Sessions recused himself ,","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"which he should n't have done .","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"Or he should have told me","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"[ before I appointed him ] .","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"`` Even my enemies say","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"that Jeff Sessions should have told you","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"that he was going to recuse himself ,","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"and then you would n't have put him in .","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"He took the job","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"and then he said","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"I 'm going to recuse myself .","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"I said :","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"'What kind of a man is this ? ' `` You know the only reason","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"I gave him the job ?","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"Because I felt loyalty ,","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"he was an original supporter .","depth":15},{"id":72,"text":"He was on the campaign .","depth":15},{"id":73,"text":"He knows","depth":15},{"id":74,"text":"there was no collusion . ''","depth":15},{"id":75,"text":"Jeff Sessions was originally brought into the Trump campaign","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"because of his hardline views on immigration .","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"A stubborn man , Mr Sessions fought for decades for anti-immigration policies .","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"Still , he has a gentle manner .","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"I 've seen him greeting colleagues with a shy smile at White House events .","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"Mr Trump prides himself on never giving up ,","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"and he admires grit and determination in others","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"- and found those traits in Mr Sessions .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"But now he is driving President Trump crazy .","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"Mr Sessions is just as determined","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"as Mr Trump is","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"-","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"and also refuses to back down .","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"Only Mr Sessions is guided by a set of bedrock conservative principles ,","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"rather than the egotism and quicksilver impulses","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"that fuel Mr Trump 's tweets and , increasingly , his TV interviews .","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"For these reasons Mr Sessions is a formidable enemy ,","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"and the battle between these two men could be long .","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"Mr Sessions made his statement during a fraught week for the White House .","depth":5},{"id":94,"text":"Two days ago , in the most dramatic developments yet","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"linked to the Russia inquiry ,","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"former Trump campaign manager Paul Manafort was found guilty of tax and bank fraud","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"and Mr Trump 's former personal lawyer Michael Cohen pleaded guilty to crimes","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"including tax evasion , bank fraud and campaign finance violations .","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"Under oath , Cohen said","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"he had been directed by Mr Trump to organise secret payments","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"to silence two women","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"who claimed","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"they had affairs with the then Republican presidential candidate ,","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"violating campaign finance laws .","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"Mr Trump has denied","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"he broke the law .","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"The sense","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"that the president 's legal troubles are growing","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"were not dampened by Thursday 's US media reports","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"that prosecutors in the Cohen case had granted immunity from prosecution to the chairman of the company","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"that publishes the National Enquirer ,","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"David Pecker , a friend of Mr Trump .","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"In the lead-up to the 2016 presidential election , Playboy model Karen McDougal sold her story of her alleged affair with Mr Trump to the Enquirer .","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"The contract","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"she signed","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"gave the tabloid exclusive story rights","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"and banned her from talking publicly about the alleged affair .","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"The story was never published .","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"Despite the sense of crisis ,","depth":7},{"id":120,"text":"it is generally believed that the Department of Justice is very unlikely to bring charges against a sitting president .","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"And correspondents say","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"it is unlikely Mr Trump 's opponents would try to impeach him before the mid-term elections .","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"Mr Trump 's most fervent supporters , what he refers to as his `` base '' outside the political cauldron of Washington DC ,","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"seem unfazed by the latest developments .","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"During the Fox News interview","depth":7},{"id":126,"text":"that was aired on Thursday ,","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"the president :","depth":6},{"id":128,"text":"Responded to speculation","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"that he might be impeached","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"by warning","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"that any such move would damage the economy","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"Insisted","depth":8},{"id":133,"text":"that payments to two women","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"alleging","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"they had affairs with him","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"had not broken election campaign rules","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"Attacked the `` flipping '' process","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"- whereby prosecutors promise a suspect a short sentence in exchange for co-operation -","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"as `` not fair '' and something","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"that `` almost ought to be outlawed ''","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"Claimed","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"that Cohen avoided up to 20 years in jail","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"because `` if you can say something bad about Donald Trump ...","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"you 'll go down to two years or three years ,","depth":13},{"id":145,"text":"which is the deal","depth":14},{"id":146,"text":"he made ''","depth":14},{"id":147,"text":"Said","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"he would award himself an `` A-plus '' grade for his work as president so far .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":297,"left":169,"right":296,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":169,"left":156,"right":168,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":153,"right":155,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":0,"right":152,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":1,"right":151,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":151,"left":150,"right":4,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":150,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":5,"right":154,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":168,"left":164,"right":167,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":164,"left":160,"right":163,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":157,"right":159,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":157,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":158,"right":12,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":158,"left":10,